Seasonal calendar data for Sudan

seasonal_calendar.Rd

Seasonal calendar data for Sudan

seasonal_calendar

Format

A tibble with 28 rows and 4 columns

VariablesDescription
eventName of seasonal calendar event or activity
startStarting date of event/activity
endStarting date of event/activity
groupClassification/group of activity or event

Source

https://fews.net/east-africa/sudan/seasonal-calendar/december-2013

seasonal_calendar
